---
title: Lamb Rump & Red Wine Gravy for Dinner  with Burnt Basque Cheesecake for Dessert
description: Every lamb rump needs a gravy and this one is extra special with a red wine jus for a richer flavour. The carrots are getting the
special treatment too by braising them for that burst deliciousness every five-star dinner needs.
